HEADWORD: Musician
<hw>Mu*si"cian</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>musicien</ets>.]</ety> <def>One skilled in the art or science of
music; esp., a skilled singer, or performer on a musical
instrument.</def>⟦br⟧
